{"tid":317770,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"手提電腦點先可以用勁d果張graphic card","createTime":"2017-07-11T16:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T16:11:19.000Z","uid":126507,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e918ddd03666878a234d9d8c4156f1f4d97e0f47","tid":317770,"uid":126507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:20:41.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<br />\n小弟之前買左laptop<br />\n<br />\n資料係咁<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/001922_cebdd5e06d1a08966b5390ad9c33a4fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F001922_cebdd5e06d1a08966b5390ad9c33a4fc.jpg&h=93790947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我發現所有野都唔係好清<br />\n<br />\nLol要去到低階乜都無先順<br />\n<br />\n無理由咁差架<br />\n<br />\n我就懷疑佢無用到張顯示卡<br />\n<br />\n所以想問下點先make sure到佢用緊 gtx 950m?"},{"pid":"24835a17a3fa2f1184805a946df6285c9352c6d2","tid":317770,"uid":126507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415c72ab07681bb61cdb0edb0fb42f12ddf0605b","tid":317770,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:28:19.000Z","msg":"入desktop右Click睇下有冇nvidia control panel<br />\n有就Click入去manage 3d setting 禁restore<br />\n冇就去nvidia官網down driver"},{"pid":"3d835ca71cbdbd0fee91fe8dda0c998d192d8db6","tid":317770,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:31:17.000Z","msg":"laptop就禁manage 3d setting<br />\n係global setting既Preferred Graphics Processor <br />\n揀 High performance NVIDIA rocessor"},{"pid":"6b0c6273b0e60ca21fbc3e5ffcf4b975e577fa48","tid":317770,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:31:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>laptop就禁manage 3d setting<br />\n係global setting既Preferred Graphics Processor <br />\n揀 High performance NVIDIA processor</blockquote>"},{"pid":"337ba122b49c9fce